items.name: Shuten Douji (Fate GO) Character Lora
items.description:
First lora, Shuten douji from fate grand order.

Pretty damn overfit on her default outfit so I'd recommend using lower weighting, especially if you want to put her into clothes that arent NSFW. Model is pretty resistant to her being fully clothed. It's possible, but you're gonna have to work for it a bit. I did most of my testing on 0.7-0.8 but i'm pretty confident you could go lower at times.

Recommended prompts are "Oni Horns, Short hair, Purple hair, purple eyes". If her horns turn fully red add "skin covered horns"

Negative clothes tags to try include "japanese clothes", "Kimono", "open kimono", "wide sleeves", "revealing clothes", "leotard"

Surprisingly isnt very afraid of giving her larger breasts, so specify "small breasts" and/or "petite" if you want them to be accurate.

Last pic used Ekune's Pov squatting cowgirl model

items.name: ControlNet Pre-Trained Models
items.description:
STOP! THESE MODELS ARE NOT FOR PROMPTING/IMAGE GENERATION

Note: These are the OG ControlNet models - the Latest Version (1.1) Models are HERE.

These are the models required for the ControlNet extension, converted to Safetensor and "pruned" to extract the ControlNet neural network. I have tested them, and they work.

These models are embedded with the neural network data required to make ControlNet function, they will not produce good images unless they are used with ControlNet.

The original version of these models in .pth format can be found here. BUT YOU DO NOT NEED THESE .pth FILES! The files I have uploaded here are direct replacements for these .pth files!

  • control_sd15_canny

  • control_sd15_depth

  • control_sd15_hed

  • control_sd15_scribble

  • control_sd15_normal

  • control_sd15_openpose

  • control_sd15_seg

  • control_sd15_mlsd

Download these models and place them in the \stable-diffusion-webui\extensions\sd-webui-controlnet\models directory.

Note: these models were extracted from the original .pth using the extract_controlnet.py script contained within the extension Github repo.

Please consider joining my Patreon! Advanced SD tutorials, settings explanations, adult-art, from a female content creator (me!)Â patreon.com/theally - I also have a write-up of ControlNet and will be updating with the latest news/developments!

items.name: Tsukiumi - Sekirei
items.description:
Here's Sekirei's best girl. If you find yourself disliking tsundere girls you must remember that everything is the fault of those whimsy male leads that don't properly discipline them! Remember to spank your tsundere! ...unless you like to be spanked yourself then I guess you don't.

V2:

Argggghhh! My old dataset was dirty and not in the good way. I mean it is understandable for my second ever LORA but fuck you past me!

Works fine with: <lora:TsukiumiV2:0.7> tsukiumi,

I was able to isolate 2 outfits and her twin tail version. In the series there's also a blue dress but there weren't enough images to be worth it. The outfits are:

  • twintails_Tsukiumi: for her twintails guise.

  • Tsukiumi_Blue_Maid_Dress: Her blue maid outfit.

  • Tsukiumi_Black_White_Dress: Her classic outfit.

As Always I will add the tag summary inside the dataset so people can experiment.

V1:

Her hair color seems to deviate to darker tones, maybe becauser i used some manga for the training so use blonde_hair if you want to make sure.

Had good results with: <lora:Tsukiumi:.4>, (Tsukiumi), blonde_hair, big_breasts

Most loras seems to do good with .4 weight and double weight for the trigger.

items.name: Kincora  Style LoRA (6.6 MB)
items.description:
Kincora Style LoRA

This is a style LoRA inspired by Kincora's art style (https://twitter.com/KIncoraK )

Please, do not harass them and do not sell image generated with that LoRA.

I'm still doing some experiments with low net dim LoRA (8 net dim / 1 Alpha). I only trained the UNET part (without the text encoder) because I wanted it to avoid learning characters from the learning set (and reduce the risk of overfitting). I wonder if I should re-train my previous LoRAs since 160/128 dim is overkill and tend to overfit.

This LoRA was trained on 177 images (half of them are cowboy shot,upper body versions of the second half) and most of them come from Azur Lane this mean that this LoRA can generate suggestive outfits (big cleavage, swimsuit, maids,etc...) if you don't prompt an outfit.

Weight:

I only tested it at weight 1.0 but you will probably have to decrease it weight (or other LoRA weight) if you want to use it with some character LoRA (especially high dim ones)

I have not tested this on default NAI so I don't know if it's too strong for the base model.

Recommended prompt:

That LoRA doesn't have any activation prompt or recommended pormpt (this is a style LoRA and not a character one).

Maybe eyelashes for close up or portrait shot ?

Model used for the example:

AnythingV4.5

items.name: Futanari Horse Penis
items.description:
Read the "about this version" for some useful information about the lora version.

You can use, change and share any of the sample images.

If you have any suggestions, I can try to implement.

I would like to thank everyone who downloads this lora, leaves their review and opinions/suggestions.

My goal is just to be able to generate different types of characters/creatures without depending on a specific model.

About the lora versions, I always try to add more content, so the latest version will always do everything the other versions do in terms of content.

The addition of masculine content does not interfere with futa content

It is possible to make hermaphrodite boys by changing the 1girl tag to 1boy.

Sometimes fingers can be generated on the penis, after looking at which images are responsible for creating this problem, I found that some tags like "fingernails, masturbation" were missing, this causes lora to generate fingers, most of the time just by putting masturbation in the negative solves this problem, "fingers, fingernails, futanari masturbation, male masturbation" should have the same effect. An example:

I also found that the "realistic" tag helps to add textures to the skin, and when used in the negative (with the "3d" tag is even better) it helps with details related to anime content like proportions, eyes and mouths.

It is possible to generate the following image angles and poses, taker pov(works well in conjunction with from below), from behind/rear view(this works with centaurs too, I forgot to put the related sample image), cowboy shot, from side, sitting, standing, kneeling, lying on back, lying on stomach(rear view/from behind), leaning forward, may have more tags I'll check later.

If you have difficulties replicating any of the sample images, check the variation seed.

You can check the lora metadata for training details.

modelVersions.description:
This version is just a test to see how lora will behave with other species, and fixing some tags for better results, v14 should be out at the end of next week, after I finish tagging the rest of the images.

It should now be possible to add "cock ring" to the horse penis, all furry related content is now correctly tagged as "furry, furry female", fixed some tags related to photo angles, "cowboy shot, full body, dutch angle", all 3d renders that were tagged as "realistic" are now correctly tagged as "3d", some parameters have been changed which allows for better output quality.

Trained with some "centaur, taur" content, use with "full body" tag to avoid strange results,

multiple penises is just a result of randomness.

modelVersions.name: herm/male update
modelVersions.description:
Implemented the hermaphrodite variation uses the following caption "hermaphrodite, 1girl, horse penis, pussy, testicleless, solo," works best with "sitting, spread legs", initially only with pussy, some models may mistake it for a cat, may create standing characters , but usually it adds testicles, sometimes it will just generate an image missing the penis, I'll try to fix that in the future. Suggestion by neilarmstron12, (I'll work on trying to add a pussy-free version).

Implemented the possibility to create male characters (due to the low amount of content it might not work correctly, clothes can add breasts, nipples will certainly add breasts, I'll try to fix it in a next update). Suggestion by OtherPerspective.

Brought back the "realistic" tag after a lot of testing, can be used in the negative along with the "3d" tag to mitigate some weirdness in anime models.

If you can't replicate the result, check the esnd seed 970718, or if the variation seed is not missing.

The keyword urethra can be used to add details to the glans, if it happens to generate fingers on the penis the following tags can be used in the negative: "fingernails, masturbation, futanari masturbation, male masturbation".

I'll add some missing poses like: "lying, on side, legs up".

items.name: Fighter Jet
items.description:
This embed is designed to nudge SD towards a better fighter jet solution. Is it perfect? Far from it. I've yet to get something that is spot on and at best it produces something "fighter jet-esque" but it does seem to work better than just putting in "fighter jet" alone.

As with most things, your model and seed will really impact this. The images here were created using Deliberate 1.1 in Automatic1111, save for the last image, which was done in A1111 and Invoke with a lot of inpainting.

As always, your mileage may vary. Posting here in case it helps someone.

modelVersions.description:
This model was trained using a 120 frame animation of an F-15 fighter jet. The model was animated in Blender and rendered at 512x512 resolution. The animation was created after several failed attempts at using stock photos. I figured the lack of coherence between photos was making it hard for SD to understand the true form of the aircraft, so I animated the ship to give the best training chance possible.

I ran the training up to 10,000 steps, but found that after about 3,000 steps the model was overtrained, I wasn't getting a better F-15 image and it overpowered any prompt I put in. After several tests, it turned out that the 250 step model was actually the best. Go figure.

The "Anything" project originated from a joke among the authors of "åç´ æ³å¸". As the name of the first 1.5 volumes of "åç´ æ³å¸" is "ä¸è±¡çç" , this name was used for the project. Anything v1.0 fused all the available anime-style models at the time, while Anything 2.1 and 3.0 selectively used certain models to prevent the generation of poor quality images.

At first, I didn't know about platforms like Huggingface or Civitai, so the models were only uploaded to Baidu Netdisk. One day, a friend in a QQ group asked me if the model mentioned in the news was made by me, and I found out that the model had been uploaded to various platforms and had gained considerable popularity. Later, after learning about Huggingface and Civitai, I uploaded the models to those platforms. However, I didn't know how to use Huggingface, so someone else uploaded the models for me.

AnythingV3, as one of the earliest anime fusion models, was hyped up by various marketing accounts and self-media platforms, and was even used for "patriotic marketing". Gradually, it became popular and was considered the "best model" at that time, which led to some people selling integration packages and deceiving novices using this model. items.name: POV Imminent Penetration [1 MB]
items.description:
This is a simple concept LoRA for Imminent penetration.

I suggest using this LoRA at 0.9-1.0 weight for best results.

Always add this to the prompt with the LoRA to activate it: 1boy, penis, imminent penetration, lying, on back, spread legs.

You can combine this with my POV Doggystyle LoRA at 0.4-0.6 weight to create a Imminent penetration doggystyle effect.

  • Remove the tags - lying, on back, spread legs (optional)

  • Add the POV Doggystyle LoRA and from behind to prompt.

  • <lora:IPV1:0.9>, 1boy, penis, imminent penetration, <lora:POVDoggy:0.5>, from behind

You can also combine this with my POV Squatting Cowgirl LoRA at 0.4-0.6 weight to create a imminent penetration squatting cowgirl effect.

  • Remove the tags - lying, on back

  • Add the POV Cowgirl LoRA and squatting to prompt.

  • <lora:IPV1:0.9>, 1boy, penis, imminent penetration, spread legs, <lora:PSCowgirl:0.4>, squatting

This was trained on NAI model - I have no idea if it works on realistic models. Images were generated on Corneo's 7th Heaven Mix using the Orange Mix VAE. The last two LoRAs seemed to work with realistic models though.

Embeds and LoRA used: Bad Prompt - Bea - Afrobull Style - POV Squatting Cowgirl - POV Doggystyle - Kakure Eria Style

Be sure to leave a comment, review and check out my other stuff here - you might like it.

items.name: Moroccan Caftan
items.description:
If you'd like to support me and do more:
https://ko-fi.com/edgonkofi
If you're looking for a >>LoRA Making Tutorial<<

You have embarked into a vacation and your plane just landed at your destination, you hear a bell ringing and your pilot starts speaking

"Ladies and gentlemen,

Welcome to Morocco, North-Africa.

I sincerely hope you will enjoy your stay, enjoy the sun, beaches, mountains, culture, and especially the food.
If I may give you a recommendation, please do stop by the artisans' district and buy a caftan dress. This piece of cultural clothing is internationally renowned. Besides Morocco recently applied for the caftan to be recognized as a piece of World Heritage by UNESCO. Do not miss the opportunity to get a caftan for you or your significant other!"

---

I sincerely hope you will enjoy using this LoRA as much as I enjoyed making it. As you can see the results are beautiful and the model is very versatile and can be used in many styles.

Go ahead, use it, have fun, and make me proud of introducing you to the culture of caftan!

items.name: Megumin (KonoSuba)
items.description:
The tower of rebellion creeps upon man's world...

The unspoken faith displayed before me...

The time has come!

Now, awaken from your slumber, and by my madness, be wrought!

Strike forth,

! ! ! EXPLOSION ! ! !

I beseech you! look no further, I've compiled for you today Megumin in her classic Arch Wizard attire this LoRA aims to allow you to recreate her, and interchange her outfit with relative precision (the staff is still a wip, sry)

I recommend using this between 0.4-0.8 results may depend on scenario, and higher prompt weights can still work consistently, but this way you have more flexibility in pose as the training Data Set is so small ATM

Base Arch Wizard Attire Prompt:

megumin, kono subarashii sekai ni shukufuku wo!, 1girl, solo, hat, witch hat, brown hair, short hair with long locks, red eyes, blush, closed mouth, black choker, collarbone, flat chest, off-shoulder dress, dress, red dress, long sleeves, black gloves, fingerless gloves, belt, brown belt, gold trim, asymmetrical legwear, mismatched legwear, bandaged leg, black thighhighs,

Base Winter Attire Prompt

megumin, kono_subarashii_sekai_ni_shukufuku_wo!, 1girl, solo, winter clothes, cat ears, white hoodie, white hood, short hair, short hair with long side locks, brown hair, red eyes, red scarf, white cape, gloves, black bodysuit,

Also include this list of curated NSFW prompts into your negatives to get more consistent SFW generations

cameltoe, ass, panties, penis, nsfw

Adjustments

As I stated earlier, I PERSONALLY curated all training prompts such that only relevant, and consistent Danbooru prompts remained to maintain a certain level of controlled predictability in all generations, there's not a lot right now given the limited training set, but as time goes on, I'll begin to list this with dedicated alt outfit prompts, so please stay tuned.

HAT (ON/OFF)

  • hat, witch hat

  • no headwear

Cape

  • brown cape

Winter Clothes (Only In "Megumin Winter Outfit" LoRA)

  • winter clothes, cat ears, white hoodie, white hood, red scarf, white cape, gloves, black bodysuit

items.name: Furry Horse
items.description:
V1.1 can't generate horse dicks on its own. The example image used my horse dick LoRA.

Updated version 1.1, this version is more cooperative with other LoRAs. Like my Horse dick LoRA.
The overall style of v1.1 is slightly different from v1.
V1.1 is not completely better than v1, v1 even performs better in some cases, you can keep v1 for inpaint or generating images.
I suggest switching between the two versions flexibly.
V1.1 using the tag Horse will be more effective than v1.

Added Horse dick LoRA. Works fine with version v1.1. This set of LoRAs is exactly the same as the horse dick LoRA I released independently. Works fine on Anything-v4.5.

About Horse dick LoRA:
The Horse dick LoRA can be used to generate horse dicks, mainly used on Futanari, but can also be used on men, traps, etc.
Prompting Penis to trigger, other similar words are also useful.

This LoRA contains two versions, v1, and v1inpaint. v1 is good at generating basic images, v1inpaint is good at inpainting, but can also generate.

The inpaint version is better only used on the penis, not the overall image.

Both can be used independently, maybe you can find a way to use them that suits you.

--

Horse, equine, and equid sometimes will have bad effects, perhaps they tend to be classified as animals rather than people. Maybe there are other ways to improve.

Works well on AbyssOrange2, can also be used on similar models.

Not good at generating horse dicks, need to use other LoRAs.
